webpackJsonp([0x7a416b537148],{448:function(a,n){a.exports={data:{site:{siteMetadata:{title:"Life is a YOLO game",author:"Henry Wu"}},markdownRemark:{id:"/home/circleci/project/src/pages/inherited-model-in-factory-girl.md absPath of file >>> MarkdownRemark",html:'<h2>問題</h2>\n<p>例如以下 Ruby on Rails 程式碼。</p>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="ruby">\n      <pre class="language-ruby"><code class="language-ruby"><span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Member</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> <span class="token constant">ActiveRecord</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token constant">Base</span>\n  <span class="token comment"># has a string column named `email`</span>\n<span class="token keyword">end</span>\n\n<span class="token keyword">class</span> <span class="token class-name">Admin</span> <span class="token operator">&lt;</span> <span class="token constant">Member</span>\n  <span class="token comment"># ...</span>\n<span class="token keyword">end</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p><code class="language-text">Member</code> 與 <code class="language-text">Admin</code> 兩個 Rails model 之間有繼承關係，那它們的 <code class="language-text">factory_girl</code> Factory 要怎麼寫呢？</p>\n<h2>解答</h2>\n<div class="gatsby-highlight" data-language="ruby">\n      <pre class="language-ruby"><code class="language-ruby"><span class="token constant">FactoryGirl</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>define <span class="token keyword">do</span>\n  factory <span class="token symbol">:member</span> <span class="token keyword">do</span> <span class="token comment"># Member model 的 factory</span>\n    email <span class="token punctuation">{</span> <span class="token constant">Faker</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span><span class="token constant">Internet</span><span class="token punctuation">.</span>email <span class="token punctuation">}</span>\n  <span class="token keyword">end</span>\n\n  factory <span class="token symbol">:admin</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> <span class="token keyword">class</span><span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token constant">Owner</span><span class="token punctuation">,</span> parent<span class="token punctuation">:</span> <span class="token symbol">:member</span>\n<span class="token keyword">end</span></code></pre>\n      </div>\n<p>如果照著以上 code 定義 factory，則 <code class="language-text">Owner</code> 的 factory 會繼承 <code class="language-text">Member</code> factory 定義的所有欄位 (例如 <code class="language-text">email</code>)。</p>\n<p>參考資料：<a href="http://stackoverflow.com/q/13343876">how to define factories with a inheritance user model</a></p>',excerpt:"問題 例如以下 Ruby on Rails 程式碼。  與   兩個 Rails model 之間有繼承關係，那它們的   Factory 要怎麼寫呢？ 解答 如果照著以上 code 定義 factory，則   的 factory 會繼承   factory…",frontmatter:{title:"如何在 factory_girl 中為有繼承關係的 Rails model 定義 Factory",date:"August 07, 2016"}}},pathContext:{slug:"/inherited-model-in-factory-girl/",previous:{fields:{slug:"/notify-after-rspec-command-finished/"},frontmatter:{title:"當 iTerm 執行完 RSpec 之後彈出通知"}},next:{fields:{slug:"/react-native-fbsdk-and-facebook-sdk/"},frontmatter:{title:"React Native, react-native-fbsdk 與 Facebook SDK"}}}}}});
